{"tid":1382964,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"想分享一隻歌比香港人","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:58:50.000Z","uid":155414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b6bd5f2d5455282c077abfac95d3be0958caf064","tid":1382964,"uid":155414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"One Ok Rock &lsquo;We are&rsquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ujR3BtB9t7Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FujR3BtB9t7Y&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=9cabd2dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ujR3BtB9t7Y</a><br />\n岩岩一路聽一路忍唔住喊<br />\nTaka個種吶喊唱出最尾個段歌詞<br />\n<em>When you&rsquo;re standing on the edge<br />\n<br />\nSo young and hopeless<br />\n<br />\nGot demons in your head<br />\n<br />\nWe are, we are<br />\n<br />\nNo ground beneath your feet<br />\n<br />\nNot here to hold you<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Cause we are, we are<br />\n<br />\nThe colors in the dark</span></strong></span></em><br />\n<br />\n如果大家因爲睇太多新聞 接受太多資訊精神支持唔住<br />\n每一個參與遊行既香港人 見到每一次既和平既集會被埋沒人性既警犬發出無數催淚彈 同暴力毒打每一個無辜既市民而覺得 憤怒 <br />\n每次政府回應都係照板煮碗 廢話連篇而對呢場運動 革命感到無力<br />\n希望你聽到呢隻歌時會重燃你心中既火<br />\n最後我只係想同大家講 我地每一個都唔係自己同孤獨 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油！光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"086d6d3d5bc2fb8158830f1309441d5cb5804427","tid":1382964,"uid":87116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"［禍不及妻兒］除暴Go上線啦！全民參與！齊齊幫老豆搵仔！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382922</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram Channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/PopomonGo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FPopomonGo&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=b142dd60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/PopomonGo</a><br />\n<br